prompt.en:
## User question
${$.data.userQuestion}

## Document (index {{_loopIndex}} of total candidates)
Title: {{_loopItem.title}}
DocId: {{_loopItem.docId}}
Source: {{_loopItem.url}}

### Content
{{_loopItem.fulltext}}

## Output
Return ONLY JSON of this shape (no prose, no markdown fences):

{
  "keyStatements": ["<concise statement the document makes that is relevant to the user question>"],
  "entities": ["<people / organisations / regulations named in the document>"],
  "position": "<one-sentence summary of the document's overall position on the question, or empty>",
  "evidenceQuotes": ["<each VERBATIM source quote used to ground a keyStatement>"],
  "quotes": [{ "text": "<each VERBATIM source quote, one entry per quote>" }]
}

The `quotes` array MUST contain the same verbatim strings as `evidenceQuotes`; it's what the downstream validator checks.

## User question
${$.data.userQuestion}

## Evidence records (structured)
{{#each _evidence}}
- Doc {{this.source.docId}} ({{this.source.title}}): {{this.extraction.data.position}} — key statements: {{this.extraction.data.keyStatements}}
{{/each}}

Write a markdown synthesis: ## Themes, ## Mehrheitslinie, ## Abweichende Aussagen, ## Offene Punkte. Cite docIds inline like (doc-123).

config.template:
# Korpus-Vollständigkeitsanalyse

## Frage

{{userQuestion}}

## Abdeckung

- **Kandidaten identifiziert:** {{coverage.candidates.total}}
- **Dokumente verarbeitet:** {{coverage.processed}}
- **Zitate geprüft:** {{coverage.quotesChecked}}
- **Zitate validiert:** {{coverage.quotesValidated}}

{{#if synthesis}}
## Synthese

{{synthesis}}
{{/if}}

{{#if evidence}}
## Per-Dokument-Evidenz

{{#each evidence}}
### {{this.source.title}}

- **DocId:** {{this.source.docId}}
- **URL:** {{this.source.url}}
- **Status:** {{this.status}}
- **Position:** {{this.extraction.data.position}}

{{#if this.extraction.data.keyStatements}}
**Kernaussagen:**
{{#each this.extraction.data.keyStatements}}
- {{this}}
{{/each}}
{{/if}}

{{#if this.quotes}}
**Zitate (validiert):**
{{#each this.quotes}}
- {{#if this.validated}}✓{{/if}}{{#if this.closestMatch}}⚠ Nicht wörtlich gefunden — nächstgelegene Passage: "{{this.closestMatch}}"{{/if}}{{#if this.text}} "{{this.text}}"{{/if}}
{{/each}}
{{/if}}

{{#if this.failures}}
**Hinweise:**
{{#each this.failures}}
- ⚠ [{{this.code}}] {{this.message}}
{{/each}}
{{/if}}

---

{{/each}}
{{/if}}
